longBusinessSummary: House Of Control Group AS develops and sells software as a service (SaaS) solutions within the areas of finance and accounting in Norway, Sweden, Denmark, and internationally. The company offers Complete Control, a cloud-based SaaS solution, which is used for managing contracts and assets, including the contracts' financial implications for accounting, budgeting, and reporting; IFRS 16 Compliance that is for assisting companies in complying with IFRS 16 requirements; and Complete Procure, which is organization's own web shop, where employees purchase at a lower cost, paperwork is automatic, and the supplier does the routine work. It also offers Digital Signature, a verified digital identity solution; Security labels, which are used for safeguard PCs and other equipment; Authority Matrix, a user-friendly cloud application that shows who has the authority to do what and it is easy to update; Supplier Portal, a sustainable and smart fix to keep down complexity and work-load when the number of suppliers grow; Supplier Invoice, a turbo for IFS users, making invoice management better and more efficient; and Effectplan, a budgeting and forecasting tool that enables you to easily and accurately create, manage, and modify the budget. The company was founded in 2013 and is headquartered at HÃ¸vik, Norway.
